Smartsheet.com, Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 12:22 PM ET
Internet Software and Services

Company Overview of Smartsheet.com, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Smartsheet.com, Inc., a Software-as-a-Service company, offers an enterprise-ready cloud app for work management and collaboration. The company provides Smartsheet, an online project management solution for Google Apps and Salesforce. Its solutions include project management, IT and operations, sales, marketing, company management, product development, human resources, finance, and specialty; and services include support, consulting, and training. The company serves small and medium businesses, Fortune 500 companies, academic institutions, and local and federal government agencies, as well as construction, consulting, education, energy/oil and gas, financial services, government, healthcare, ...
Smartsheet.com, Inc., a Software-as-a-Service company, offers an enterprise-ready cloud app for work management and collaboration. The company provides Smartsheet, an online project management solution for Google Apps and Salesforce. Its solutions include project management, IT and operations, sales, marketing, company management, product development, human resources, finance, and specialty; and services include support, consulting, and training. The company serves small and medium businesses, Fortune 500 companies, academic institutions, and local and federal government agencies, as well as construction, consulting, education, energy/oil and gas, financial services, government, healthcare, high tech, legal, manufacturing, marketing, media, nonprofit, software, retail, and restaurant/hospitality markets. Smartsheet.com, Inc. was formerly known as Navigo Technologies, Inc. The company was founded in 2005 and is based in Bellevue, Washington.
Detailed Description


10500 NE 8th StreetSuite 1300Bellevue, WA 98004-4357United StatesFounded in 2005



